snippet.title: Terara Network
snippet.description: We were founded on September 26, 2020 by vetran Ethiopian journalist Tamerat Negera Feyisa as a platform for exploring, defining & promoting Ethiopianist ideas through quality web based journalism & commentary. Terara aspires to discuss issues in Politics, Economics, Education, Arts & Letters of Ethiopia & the greater horn. The seed money to start Terara was raised by Tamerat’s friend, Tariku Geleta through crowd funding campaign on December 8, 2019 that enabled Tamerat’s fans around the world to be connected for a common cause of founding an Ethiopianist media in the public sphere.

snippet.title: Tigrai Media House
snippet.description: TMH’s mission is to enrich the lives of Tigray people by providing captivating media through nonpartisan journalism. TMH will promote community dialogue through exchanging information across different social, cultural, geographical, regional, and ideological boundaries. This dialogue will assist in TMH’s endeavor to enhance tolerance, social integration, and mutual coexistence among all east African people.

snippet.title: ኢትዮ ሰላም  Ethio Selam
snippet.description:
ስለ ሰላም እናወራለን!!!

ስለ ሰላም እንሞግታለን!!!

ኢትዮ-ሰላም በኢትዮጵያ ውስጥ አውንታዊ ሰላም ሰፍኖ ማየትን የሚፈልግ፤ የአገራችንን ማህበረ-ኢኮኖሚያዊና ፖለቲካዊ ጉዳዮች ከተለያዩ እይታዎች አንፃር የሚተነተኑበትና አውንታዊ ሰላምንና መረጋጋትን ሊያሰፍኑና ሊያመጡ የሚችሉ አማራጭ ሀሳቦች የሚቀርቡበት ነፃና ገለልተኛ ሚዲያ ነው።

ይህን እንቅስቃሴ ማበረታታትና በአገራችን አውንታዊ ሰላም ሰፍኖ ማየት የምትናፍቁ ሁሉ ሚዲያችንን ሰብስክራይብ በማድረግ ቤተሰብ እንዲሆኑንና በሚችሉት ሁሉ እንዲያግዙን ጥሪ እናደርጋለን።

Ethio-Selam is a free and independent media that seeks to analyze the socio-economic and political issues of our country from different perspectives and offers alternative ideas that can bring about positive peace and stability in our country Ethiopia.

We encourage all those who want to help for this movement and yearn to see the positive peace in our country to subscribe to our media and become a family and help us in any way you can.

snippet.title: EVN for Ethiopia
snippet.description:
Welcome to Ethio Voice Network (EVN)- Your hub of information focusing on Ethiopia and the Horn of Africa.

EVN has a clear vision – to empower our audience with reliable and timely information. We are dedicated to delivering up-to-date, accurate, balanced, and objective news to keep you informed and engaged.

Our unwavering commitment to truth is reflected in our motto: “In Truth We Trust.” As a frontline media platform, you can rely on EVN to provide trustworthy and credible news, analysis, and views. Our mission is to be your go-to source of news and information on Ethiopia. Join us on this journey as we strive to become the foremost destination for insightful and comprehensive coverage.

At EVN, we value your voice and actively encourage your participation. We believe that diverse perspectives, expertise, and tips enrich our platform and contribute to a vibrant and informed community.

snippet.title: ebstv worldwide
snippet.description:
EBS TV is a privately held media company established in 2008 in Silver Spring, MD, USA to provide a niche transmission programming that targets the booming Ethiopian market globally. Since its formation EBS has been, and still is, providing its media to subscribers interested to access programming of Ethiopian history, culture lifestyle, sports, entertainment, tourism, and business.
EBS TV aims to promote Ethiopian and other African countries values, cultures and traditions globally. The much-needed information provided by EBS TV would help bridge the cultural divide and narrow the communication gap for Ethiopians residing in North America and around the world. EBS TV also envisions providing programs pertaining to the rich cultural heritage of Ethiopia, its history, tradition, socio-economic development, business, tourism and current affairs.

For More information on the EBS TV
EBS TV / Ethiopian Broadcasting Service

info@ebstv.tv
www.ebstv.tv

snippet.title: DW Amharic
snippet.description:
ስለ ኢትዮጵያ እና መላው ዓለም በየቀኑ ከመሀል አውሮጳ የምናስተላልፈውን የዕለቱን ዋና ዋና ዜና ለማድመጥ አለያም ለመመልከት ይከተሉን ። ዶይቸ ቬለ (DW) በዓለም የሚከሰቱ የሰበር ዜና መረጃዎችን ከስር መሰረታቸው በጥልቀት በመፈተሽ ያቀርባል ። ተመልካቾቻችን ጉዳዬ የሚሏቸውን ርእሰ ጉዳዮች ወኪሎቻችን ከቦታው ዝርዝር ትንታኔ በመሥራት ያቀርባሉ ። ዶይቸ ቬለ በ30 ቋንቋዎች የሚያሰራጭ የጀርመን ዓለም አቀፍ ጣቢያ ነው ። በኢትዮጵያ፤ በአፍሪቃ እና መላው ዓለም የሚከሰቱ ማኅበራዊ፤ ፖለቲካዊ እና ኤኮኖሚያዊ መረጃዎችን የጀርመን እና የሌሎች ምልከታዎችን በማሰናሰል በገለልተኛነት እንዘግባለን ። በአፍሪቃ ቀንድ፦ በኤርትራ፣ ሶማሊያ፣ ሱዳን፣ ጅቡቲ  የሚከሰቱ ጉዳዮችን እንዘግባለን ።

ዶይቸቬለ በተለያዩ ሰዎች እና ባሕሎች መካከል ያሉ ልዩነቶች ግንዛቤ እንዲያገኙ አበረታታለሁ ብሎ ተስፋ ያደርጋል ። በጀርመን መንግሥት የገንዘብ ድጋፍ ቢያገኝም የዶይቸ ቬለ ሥራ ቁጥጥር የሚደረግበት በዶይቸ ቬለ ደንብ ነው ። ያ ማለት ዘገባዎቻችን ምንጊዜም ከመንግሥት ጫና ነጻ ናቸው ። እዚህ የምትሰጧቸው አስተያየቶችን እና የምታደርጓቸው ውይይቶች ንጹሕ እና በመከባበር ላይ የተመሠረቱ እንዲሆኑ በትህትና እንጠይቃለን ። ለተጨማሪ መረጃ ከታች የሚገኘውን የዶይቸ ቬለ የሥነ-ምግባር ደንብ (Netiquette) መመልከት ትችላላችሁ ።

snippet.title: VOA Amharic
snippet.description:
ቪኦኤ-አማርኛ በዲጂታል፣ በራዲዮና በቴሌቪዥን ዜናና ዘገባዎችን ለአድማጭና ለተመልካች ያቀርባል።

ከመቶ አሥር ሚሊየን በላይ የሚገመት ህዝብ ያላት ኢትዮጵያ የመንግሥት የሥራ ቋንቋ አማርኛ ነው።  ቪኦኤ አማርኛን ከአዋቂው ህዝብ አንድ አምስተኛ የሚሆነው  እንደሚያዳምጥ በቅርቡ የተካሄዱ ቅኝቶች አሳይተዋል። ይህ የአድማጭ ቁጥር ቪኦኤ ከሚያሠራጭባቸው ማንኛውቸም ቋንቋዎች አድማጭ ቁጥር እጅግ የሰፋው ነው።

ቪኦኤ-አማርኛ ስለ ኢትዮጵያ፣ ኤርትራ፣ አፍሪካ፣ ዩናይትድ ስቴትስ እና ዓለም አቀፍ በዲጂታል፣ በራዲዮና በቴሌቪዥን ዜናና ዘገባዎችን ለአድማጭና ለተመልካች ያቀርባል።

VOA Amharic reaches our audience on digital, radio, and TV, delivering news and content about Ethiopia, Eritrea, Africa and United States. We will also be bringing you Health Shows, Youth Shows, Democracy Field, Women’s Shows, Sports Shows on different days, stay tuned.

330 Independence Ave SW
Washington, D.C. 20237
+1 (202) 205-9942 Ext 14

snippet.title: Dawit Dreams
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube channel of Dawit Dreams.

Dawit Dreams is a life couch and Author of "ትልቅ ሕልም አለኝ" book. His book "ትልቅ ሕልም አለኝ" has been sold more than 80,000 copies and available in all book stores.

He has empowered more than 5 million Ethiopians throughout the world by face-to-face classes, Government office training programs, educational Podcast, educational videos, morning quotes and now with live events. For more than six years, thousands of people have enjoyed the warmth, humor, and transformational power of Dawit Dreams personal development class.

snippet.title: MERI PODCAST
snippet.description:
Meri Podcast is an Ethiopian business podcast hosted by entrepreneurs Kenean and Tigabu featuring the greatest entrepreneurs and uncovering what made them successful.

Meri Podcast's vision is to build a strong and vibrant private sector in Ethiopia and beyond, through storytelling and content creation. We aspire to be the leading source of knowledge, inspiration, and education for entrepreneurs and executives, helping them to achieve their goals and transform the economy. We invite you to be part of the new movement.

snippet.title: Donkey Tube
snippet.description:
Donkey Tube is a Media Company that mainly focuses on echoing a voice to the voiceless, donkey tube has been working hard in raising awareness in different sociological matters for the last 3 and more years. holding more than 40 employees in it's realm, this media company has been the reason for the change of so many lives throughout the country.

Comedian Eshetu Melese meticulously brought this company from the start with his colleagues. Comedian Eshetu is an Ethiopian based Standup Comedian, Entrepreneur and philanthropist who devoted his life in to making this world a better place. he created stages and made his own voice heard by so many people raising awareness by disguising it via humor and comedy.

snippet.title: Ghion TV Multimedia
snippet.description: Ghion Satalite Television (GTV) is a private media which is established in 2024 by the renowned journalist Minalachew Simachew who has a 20 years of proven experiance in brodcast media.. GTV advocates for the survival of the Amhara people by refuting the false narrative that was preached against Amhara by different anti Ethiopia forces for decades. Ghion Television is a well-founded and authentic media platform through satellite television and short-wave radio stations. All or some of the programs streamed on Ghion Television outlets will also be shared on different social media platforms such as YouTube, Facebook, tweeter, tikt0k ,rumble etc.
